rule_text: If a lure combination has a blue shape, it will catch fish.
If a lure combination has a yellow shape or a diamond on the bottom, it will catch fish.
If a lure combination has colors that are more visible under water (red, yellow), it will catch fish.
If a lure combination has a pointy shape on the bottom, it will catch fish.
If a lure combination has a four-pointed star, it will catch fish.
If a lure combination has a yellow or red shape with a purple dot, it will catch fish
If a lure combination is shaped more like a fish, it will catch fish.
There is no pattern to which lure combinations catch fish: the results are random, but there are approximately equal numbers that catch fish and donâ€™t.
